I have added a shell-specific `blockedOperators` setting to the config in version `0.1.8`. You can pass a list of operators to be blocked (if `enableInjectionProtection` is set to `true`):

```json
{
  "security": {
    "enableInjectionProtection": true
  }
  "cmd": {
        "enabled": true,
        "command": "cmd.exe",
        "args": ["/c"],
        "blockedOperators": ["&", "|", ";", "`"]
  }
}
```

Let me know if this doesn't solve the issue, otherwise I'll consider this solved and close.

